Call PictureSnapConvert(Int(2), formx!, formy!, formz!, RealTimeMotorPositions!(XMotor%), RealTimeMotorPositions!(YMotor%), RealTimeMotorPositions!(ZMotor%), fractionx!, fractiony!)
If ierror Then Exit Sub

