If ierror Then Exit Function

Call PictureSnapConvert(Int(2), formx2!, formy2!, formz2!, CSng(0#), temp!, CSng(0#), fractionx2!, fractiony2!)
If ierror Then Exit Function

temp! = Abs(formy2! - formy1!)
End If

PictureSnapConvertStageDistancetoImageDistance! = temp!

Exit Function

' Errors
